"Mae Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov wedi achosi anaf, cyffro, a dinistr i deuluoedd a ffrindiau Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, ac Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", meddai'r datganiad o'r nod.
